show.title: The Hidden Hero

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/ceXN5n
show.description: When a principled ex-commander hiding as a humble café worker saves a ruthless yet elegant CEO from a late-night assault, she tests his character with a fake marriage to uncover his weakness—but as secrets surface and enemies close in, their staged relationship turns into a high-stakes game of power, loyalty, and unexpected love.
